    "TripoSR and Mistral 7B showed strong performance in comprehensiveness, indicating their ability to provide wide-ranging and detailed explanations, although they had areas for improvement in fidelity and sufficiency.",
    "GemMoE-Beta-1 was notable for its high sufficiency scores, efficiently conveying essential information for user comprehension of model decisions.",
